<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Payroll Processed - <%= companyName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fb;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #003366;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #e0f0ff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #003366;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #003366;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <% if (logoUrl) { %>
        <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="<%= companyName %> Logo" height="40" style="margin-bottom: 10px;" />
      <% } %>
      <h2>Payroll Processed - <%= month %> <%= year %></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

      <p>The payroll for <strong><%= staffName %></strong> has been successfully processed for 
      <strong><%= month %> <%= year %></strong>.</p>

      <p>You can review and download the processed payroll files below:</p>

